  <brief_title>Aortic Dimensions in Turner Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>Aortic Dimensions, 24hour Ambulatory Blood Pressure and Sympathovagal Tone in Turner Syndrome. In Relation to Aortic Dilatation and Dissection.</official_title>
